http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: Montana K-12 Technology Content Standards Framework

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The Technology Content Standards Framework is a set of agreements, rationales, and rules that provides the foundation for standards-based Technology education in Montana. This framework is the blueprint for further development of key components, such as Essential Learning Expectations, Performance Rubrics, and curriculum.
